<font color="#FF0000">THE WALL 1997</font><br>
<tt>Mon Jul 21 22:30:03 US/Eastern 1997
</tt><p>
As I stood here in front of the wall on this Memorial day,1997,a thought came to me.I have heard som viet nam vets.say,that they feared that they would be forgotten.As I  gaze into the black wall,and see the reflections of hundreds of people,a small voice comes to me.It said&quot;I THINK NOT&quot;  I backed up a couple of steps and looked around,I saw young people and old all around.I saw Viet Nam vets.telling their stories,and everyone listened.I looked around and saw over 200 years of history standing around me.   So now when someone asks me if I think Viet Nam vets. will be forgotten I will have to say,    &quot;I THINK NOT&gt;&quot;
